{"tid":768890,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底拍拖係咩feel","createTime":"2018-08-05T18:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T06:15:28.000Z","uid":28696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0b3ced353d7c64f4671f8fd18b08c978932693a0","tid":768890,"uid":28696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:46:22.000Z","msg":"踏入2字頭本身一個人都好地地<br />\n冇話特別想拍拖<br />\n點知早2日發夢有條囡同自己表白仲要拖住手行街<br />\nsweet到漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n瞓醒個下先知原來係場夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底現實拍拖係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445980641bcde66ce20000c9f56421cb30a3d5a0","tid":768890,"uid":24971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:50:12.000Z","msg":"照下鏡先啦<br />\n<br />\n又要想拍拖又唔撚執下自己<br />\n<br />\n著衫柒 談吐悶 皮膚差 生得矮 頭又油 錢又無<br />\n<br />\n搞點上面四樣再呻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4966c3f3640d82717ff8a2fcaaffa81e2fc7b58c","tid":768890,"uid":28696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:53:32.000Z","msg":"問下都要比你屌 抵你一世無拖拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0b00aea77cb132011b14c47ba0c9cf171bf2e0","tid":768890,"uid":49055,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/06/025418_d1bfc47b6221e470f173ecaa3c317d10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F025418_d1bfc47b6221e470f173ecaa3c317d10.png&h=3f2358b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9da6520a226ae28cd49cfa9b58fd49217cf74b9d","tid":7688